{"id": 3088, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年初给自己列的愿望清单，你都达成了哪一条？", "description": "又到了一年一度审视自我的时候。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 651, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191212154708BK4V0fkEZuvGIbr6.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-12T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 350467, "content": "就当完成了就好了，不然太累了，然而并没有什么卵用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141030}, {"id": 350469, "content": "1.不要熬夜。\n2.每天看十页书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668209}, {"id": 350470, "content": "还在努力冲冲冲之中～\n什么播放量1W呀～\n6个月生存存款呀～\n种一颗胡杨～\n每个月的读书呀～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557719}, {"id": 350472, "content": "看书，顺利换了工作步入正轨，教资证备考过了一门", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632613}, {"id": 350480, "content": "哼╭(╯^╰)╮说了要好好学习，早睡早起，不要熬夜的，然后……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673871}, {"id": 350485, "content": "瘦了10几斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478843}, {"id": 350487, "content": "写了半年的一日一记手帐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 350492, "content": "把买的书都看完\n确实做到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136293}, {"id": 351004, "content": "没立flag～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675270}, {"id": 350511, "content": "考上一本。\n一本是考上了结果还是复读了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674584}, {"id": 351285, "content": "我明年考上研究生\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469370}, {"id": 351038, "content": "活到过年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829353}, {"id": 350534, "content": "多关心家庭。渐渐有在多关心哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601494}, {"id": 352330, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350816, "content": "脱单，然后又单身。减肥倒是成功减了10斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674877}, {"id": 350564, "content": "干嘛那么残忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 350565, "content": "安全渡过本命年欣惠", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113901}, {"id": 350571, "content": "买了块表", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662589}, {"id": 351084, "content": "一门HD\nCFA一级", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675495}, {"id": 350573, "content": "2018年12月的时候参加了网易的立flag活动，只写了四条，居然在2019年全部达成。本来忘了的，结果年底瘦身数字接近目标的时候，忽然想起来当初立下的四条。很有成就感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674647}, {"id": 351085, "content": "开始早睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675446}, {"id": 350834, "content": "考上研了，玩的挺嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674899}, {"id": 350584, "content": "每月支出小于每月收入", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674026}, {"id": 350334, "content": "虽然没完全达成减重十斤，但总算勉强做到了没有增重", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350336, "content": "给自己列的书单，最后三个月紧赶慢赶总算基本看完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350595, "content": "一件件想起来觉得小有成就的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 350598, "content": "给自己定了不熬夜，按时睡按时起。勉强达成！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135705}, {"id": 350343, "content": "改变消费习惯，少买了很多自己根本用不上的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350599, "content": "顺利毕业，熬过了最低落的时间，找到了份还不错的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674670}, {"id": 350345, "content": "努力了一年，拖延症虽然还没有根治，但也有所改善", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350871, "content": "失去了努力变好的勇气，整天混吃等死，脾气暴躁\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298141}, {"id": 350632, "content": "去欧洲学滑雪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313622}, {"id": 350395, "content": "已经忘记都立了哪些flag啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 247, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613325}, {"id": 350397, "content": "处理了闲置化妆品和物品，不再盲目跟风买化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674404}, {"id": 350398, "content": "抓紧时间复习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674320}, {"id": 350400, "content": "学习 学习技能 赚钱 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1627500}, {"id": 350401, "content": "跑了个全马。虽然跑完后几乎瘸了一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303406}, {"id": 350402, "content": "认真的做了手账！买了第一个胶卷机！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574994}, {"id": 350915, "content": "还有十多天，不急", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586458}, {"id": 351171, "content": "好歹走到了暴食症阴影的边缘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821351}, {"id": 350404, "content": "做一点新的尝试，走出舒适区", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588809}, {"id": 350409, "content": "终于离开了单身狗的团队啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810127}, {"id": 350410, "content": "又到了一年一度不敢审视自我的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20191213101007toew7fJMLOqRASur.jpg", "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666475}, {"id": 350412, "content": "“列了一个清单”", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373628}, {"id": 350413, "content": "看完了《罗马人的故事》和《雪中悍刀行》。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954920}, {"id": 350670, "content": "第三年考研了，qswl", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755738}, {"id": 350415, "content": "学车哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665375}, {"id": 350927, "content": "去年没立，今年打算开始立了哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20191219152536HRbiE1dhg2zWrm4C", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515557}, {"id": 350417, "content": "都没有达成", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428458}, {"id": 350418, "content": "看书30本，去三个陌生城市", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}]}